ojc.bain - package ojc.bain
Bain - a neural network simulator.
ojc.bain.base - package ojc.bain.base
Contains the base classes from which most of the components of a simulation are built on or extend from.
ojc.bain.misc - package ojc.bain.misc
Contains miscellaneous utility classes and functions.
ojc.bain.neuron - package ojc.bain.neuron
Contains classes that implement neuron models.
ojc.bain.synapse - package ojc.bain.synapse
Contains classes that implement synapse models.
ojc.bain.test - package ojc.bain.test
Contains miscellaneous classes used for testing and analysis.
output - Variable in class ojc.bain.test.Test3
 
outputsAreStale() - Method in class ojc.bain.base.ComponentCollection
Returns true iff the output values of the components, provided by ComponentCollection.getOutput(int index) and ComponentCollection.getOutputs() have become stale due to being altered on remote execution hardware (eg GPU) and not yet being fetched back.
outputsStale - Variable in class ojc.bain.base.ComponentCollection
Flag to indicate if the outputs as calculated in an Aparapi kernel have been modified on the GPU (and so would need to be transferred back if we're interested in looking at their values).
